    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA280-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu vāyil vēṇṭic ceṉṟa tōḻikkut talaimakaḷ maṟuttu moḻintatu. 2. talaimakaṉai ēṟṟukkoṇṭu vaḻippaṭṭāḷaip pukaḻntu pukka tōḻikkut talaimakaḷ colliyatūumām.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is what SHE said in refusal to the confidante who had gone wishing to mediate. 2. It is also what SHE said to the confidante who had entered praising her who was on the way of admitting HIM.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA280">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            kokkiṉuk koḻinta tīmpaḻaṅ kokkiṉ</l>
<l>            kūmpunilai yaṉṉa mukaiya vāmpaṟ</l>
<l>            ṟūṅkunīrk kuṭṭattut tuṭumeṉa vīḻun</l>
<l>            taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ ṟaṇṭāp parattamai</l>
<l>            pulavā yeṉṟi tōḻi pulavēṉ </l>
<l>            paḻaṉa yāmaip pācaṟaip puṟattuk</l>
<l>            kaḻaṉi kāvalar cuṭunan tuṭaikkun</l>
<l>            toṉṟumutir vēḷir kuṉṟū raṉṉaveṉ</l>
<l>            ṉaṉmaṉai naṉivirun tayaruṅ</l>
<l>            kaitū viṉmaiyi ṉeytā māṟē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>“Are you not vexed,”</l>
<l rend="indent3">you said, friend,</l>
<l>“about the going astray, unpreventable,</l>
<l rend="indent2">of the man from the village by the cool ghat,</l>
<l rend="indent2">where the sweet fruits left to drop by the mango tree fall with</l>
<l rend="indent2">a splash(?) into the depth of water on which are suspended</l>
<l rend="indent">white waterlilies with buds as the closed[-wings] state of a heron?”</l>
<l rend="indent3">I am not vexed,</l>
<l rend="indent2">because I don’t get [him], for there [is] no leisure,</l>
<l rend="indent3">while my good house is well engaged in a feast,</l>
<l rend="indent4">as the hill village of the venerable<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">toṉṟu mutir</term>: "old old" presumably means something like "venerable".</note> Vēḷir,</l>
<l rend="indent3">where the field guards are breaking roasted snails</l>
<l rend="indent4">on the fortified backs of the tortoises in the tank.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
